To create from scratch:

1) npm init: just press enter in all options
2) npm i express
3) create index.js file(copy the existing one)
4) node index.js: try to connect to the generated server
5) open browser: type: localhost:2000 - if you got a message saying Cannot Get, it means that it's working
6) create a home file within the lib directory
7) within the android directory, app directory, build.gradle change line 30 and 52 to compileSdkVersion 33 and targetSdkVersion 33 respectvly